{
  "stem": "11801.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was not exactly the pliable child that she may have known when I was eight, when I was a little child.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was now an adult, although to her I was still a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Bonding I don't believe ever happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We superficially were a family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In reality, I don't think we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had many problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First of all, I was terribly unhappy in the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I hated it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I came, you know, thinking that all my problems would be solved, that nothing-- you know, that there would not be any more negative experiences, that I somehow would sail along, go to school, have a career, and get married, and, you know, all the sort of stuff that you read in, in fairy tales-- that all this would happen, simply because that's the only way of life that is possible in these great United States.",
      "word_count": 76
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was very naive, but I didn't know any-- you know, and I didn't know anything else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I went to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I came to the United States, I know, you know, I had theoretically lost three years of schooling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, in their wisdom, the school-- Bassick High School, in Bridgeport, Connecticut-- decided to sort of-- I was the first foreigner that came to that school without knowing English.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And eventually two more kids came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this was a totally new experience for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they decided to just send me to English classes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I went from one English class to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I lost another year, in fact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So, by the end of that year, I was now four years behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I sort of fibbed my way through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had brought no records.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
